lemma foo31: "\<forall>r. r \<in> set p \<and> x \<in> dom (C r) \<longrightarrow> r = AllowPortFromTo a b po \<or> r = DenyAllFromTo a b \<or> r = DenyAll \<Longrightarrow> set p = set s \<Longrightarrow> \<forall>r. r \<in> set s \<and> x \<in> dom (C r) \<longrightarrow> r=AllowPortFromTo a b po \<or> r = DenyAllFromTo a b \<or> r = DenyAll"
